Release Notes
Added partial take‑profit functionality to help reduce drawdowns and improve overall trade stability.

Introduced enhanced visual elements, including trend‑based shading and clearer event markers, to make the script’s behavior easier to understand at a glance.
Feb 17
Release Notes
Added transparent Take‑Profit and Break‑Even lines to improve clarity and provide better visual tracking of trade management levels. These levels now appear dynamically and disappear when no longer active, making the chart easier to read and interpret.
